HEADWORD: Whorled
<hw>Whorled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Furnished with whorls;
arranged in the form of a whorl or whorls; verticillate; <as>as,
<ex>whorled</ex> leaves</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

